                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14093706" author="JIRAUSER308715" created="Tue, 12 Aug 2014 04:19:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patches for 2.0 and 2.1 to put back the &quot;just throw the memtables away&quot; code if durable writes is false and auto snapshot is false.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14094062" author="tjake" created="Tue, 12 Aug 2014 13:50:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;LGTM&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14094071" author="benedict" created="Tue, 12 Aug 2014 14:01:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;d rather we did not reintroduce the &apos;renew memtable&apos; method, as it is inherently dangerous. If we are to do so, it should have clear danger warnings around it, OR it should explicitly clear the CL of any records it contains.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14094095" author="tjake" created="Tue, 12 Aug 2014 14:28:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;committed with an assert in 2.0 that renewMemtable is only called with durable_writes false&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14094124" author="JIRAUSER308715" created="Tue, 12 Aug 2014 14:54:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch to be applied to trunk to fix the tests that weren&apos;t updated on merge for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-6968&quot; title=&quot;Reduce Unit Test Times Due to Schema Loading&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-6968&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-6968&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
